name: Lettering #004: Keep Going
description:
“Let's Keep Going, You Got This!”
I made this piece to comfort myself. My work is my safe space, including this piece. With it, I remind myself to keep going for what matters to me.

7 fps | 4000x4000px

Using Procreate App on iPad Pro
